  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FieldReader<FieldType>
    This interface deserializes a field from binary data
    FieldVisibilityHandler<RowType,FieldType>
    This class must be implemented to perform per field value visibility decisions.
    FieldWriter<RowType,FieldType>
    This interface serializes a field's value into a byte array
